Package com.BrickBreaker.gui

Class GameModel

java.lang.Object
com.BrickBreaker.gui.GameModel
public class GameModel
extends java.lang.Object
This is the GameModel class that store the variable used for GameController and GameView class. The wall class is renamed to GameModel class as it contains most of the data to generate the game.
Since:
3/11/2021
Version:
1.0
Author:
Alden Sia Zheng Heng
